# Chess Platform: Premium UI Upgrade + Unique Features

The platform already has a solid React/TypeScript/Tailwind glassmorphism base. The goal is to **dramatically elevate the UI** to rival chess.com and Lichess, and add **5 unique USP features** no other platform offers — all frontend-only so they work without backend changes.

---

## 🎯 Unique Selling Point Features (USPs)

These are features that differentiate this platform:

| Feature | Description | Why it's unique |
|---|---|---|
| **🧠 Tilt Meter** | A live meter tracking your blunder streaks and time pressure stress | No platform shows "you're on tilt right now" warnings |
| **🎤 AI Coach Panel** | Contextual text tips after each move (deterministic, no API needed) | Real-time coaching overlay inside the game |
| **🗺️ Piece Heatmap** | Visual heatmap of piece activity in Analysis tab | Lichess has it hidden; we surface it prominently |
| **🧬 Opening DNA Card** | Your top 3 openings shown as cards with a style radar chart | No platform shows your "chess DNA" visually |
| **⚡ ELO Predictor** | Estimates your potential ELO gain/loss before a game starts | Completely novel feature for motivation |

---

