### USP Features (New Components)

#### [NEW] [TiltMeter.tsx](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/others/minor%20project/chess-main/apps/frontend/src/components/TiltMeter.tsx)
- Shows a stress meter based on consecutive blunders/mistakes or low time
- Displays "On Tilt 🔥" warning with tips panel
- Uses moves history from Recoil store

#### [NEW] [AICoachPanel.tsx](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/others/minor%20project/chess-main/apps/frontend/src/components/AICoachPanel.tsx)
- After each move, shows a contextual chess tip based on move type (capture, check, castle, etc.)
- Deterministic — uses a curated tip database, no API needed
- Shows as a floating panel in the game sidebar

#### [NEW] [Puzzles.tsx](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/others/minor%20project/chess-main/apps/frontend/src/screens/Puzzles.tsx)
- Daily challenge board with a static daily puzzle (seeded by date)
- Shows puzzle rating, theme, and streak tracker
- Uses chess.js for move validation

#### [NEW] [Profile.tsx](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/others/minor%20project/chess-main/apps/frontend/src/screens/Profile.tsx)
- Shows Opening DNA card (radar chart of opening preferences)
- ELO Predictor widget
- Mock stats displayed beautifully

#### [NEW] [EloPredictor.tsx](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/others/minor%20project/chess-main/apps/frontend/src/components/EloPredictor.tsx)
- Component shown in Game pre-game lobby
- Calculates estimated ELO delta based on opponent rating difference

