## Verification Plan

### Dev Server Check
```bash
cd "c:\Users\FARAZ KHAN\Desktop\DEKSTOP\others\minor project\chess-main\apps\frontend"
npm run dev
```
Confirm the server starts on `http://localhost:5173` with no compilation errors.

### Manual Verification (Browser)
1. Open `http://localhost:5173` → verify new Landing hero, animated background, USP feature cards
2. Sidebar → verify premium logo, active state glow, all nav items
3. Navigate to `/game/random` → verify premium player cards, timer colors, TiltMeter, AICoachPanel
4. Navigate to `/learn` → verify card grid with difficulty badges
5. Navigate to `/puzzles` → verify daily puzzle board renders
6. Navigate to `/profile` → verify Opening DNA card and EloPredictor widget
